new.name: fortileak-01-2025-Be
new.description: This repository contains informaion about the Fortigate firewall vulnerability (CVE-2022-40684) and affected data that were publicly disclosed by the Belsen Group. This information is being shared for security research and defensive purposes to help organizations identify if they were impacted.

new.description: CVE-2024-41570 is a critical SSRF vulnerability in Havoc C2 v0.7 that allows an unauthenticated attacker to send arbitrary network requests from the team server. This flaw can be exploited for internal network access or remote code execution (RCE).

update.description: Carga de archivos sin restricciones en la funcionalidad de carga de archivos grandes en `/main/inc/lib/javascript/bigupload/inc/bigUpload.php` en Chamilo LMS en versiones <= 1.11.24 permite a atacantes no autenticados realizar ataques de Cross Site Scripting almacenados y obtener cdigo remoto ejecucin mediante la carga de web shell.

update.name: Chamilo-CVE-2023-4220-Exploit
update.description: This is an Exploit for Unrestricted file upload in big file upload functionality in Chamilo-LMS for this location "/main/inc/lib/javascript/bigupload/inc/bigUpload.php" in Chamilo LMS <= v1.11.24, and Attackers can obtain remote code execution via uploading of web shell.
